### 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 获取所有用户 (需要 JWT Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 获取在线用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/online
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 发送消息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "content": "Hello, World!",
  "type": "text",
  "receiver_id": 2,
  "group_id": 0
}

### 获取消息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/login
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 获取消息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/messages?type=private&target_id=2&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 创建群组
POST http://localhost:8080/api/groups
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "测试群组",
  "description": "这是一个测试群组",
  "avatar": "https://example.com/group-avatar.jpg"
}

### 获取群组列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/groups
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 系统监控
GET http://localhost:8080/api/monitor/system
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 添加群组成员
POST http://localhost:8080/api/groups/1/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "user_id": 3
}

### 移除群组成员
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/groups/1/members/3
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 连接统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/monitor/connections
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE